most powerful us commercial rocket martin mariettas first 
commercial launch of the titan 3 on dec 31 propelled british and 
japanese communications satellites into orbit 
mcdonnell douglas launched the first us commercial rocket the 
delta which took a british satellite broadcasting satellite into 
orbit last august general dynamics plans to enter the competition 
in june with its atlas rocket 
