rosary which has neither pews nor elaborate paintings on the 
walls and thought this is it 
then one of the blind parishioners tugged at her dress and asked 
her if she would bring him a cup of coffee i knew then i was in 
the right place lee said 
the church which is about 60 percent white 25 percent black 
and 15 percent asian also proved its viability by certifying its 
speakers and eucharistic ministers through the archdiocese 
