their report recommended the church use more approved texts 
train lay ministers on the meaning of liturgical symbols and 
gestures and reevaluate the practice of allowing parishioners to 
dip communion hosts into the wine which is supposed to be sipped 
overall kidd thought the report was fair 
its like they wanted us to hear the lecture and once we heard 
the lecture it was ok just so that we knew what should be he 
said 
