welloff diners 
theyre too small and theres too many of them for the 
government to shut down said one young woman 
private businessmen have little overhead and many have enough 
savings to weather a few bad years as long as theyre not hounded 
and harassed out of existence 
sun lili too young to remember the cultural revolution said 
shes not worried 
im not selling anything bad she said fingering a 
velvetcovered headband 
